content.text: What is the stiffness matrix for this part of the groove structure?

The red circle indicates a groove positioned at the entrance. This position demands movement along the Z-axis, with high stiffness in the Z direction and low stiffness in the X and Y directions.

### Stiffness Matrix

  "stiffness_matrix": [
    [100, 0, 0],
